statements: SELECT * FROM incidents
SELECT incident_id, incident_type, incident_time FROM incidents WHERE vehicle_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000'
SELECT incident_id, incident_description FROM incidents WHERE incident_type = 'Accident' ORDER BY incident_time DESC
SELECT incident_id, incident_location FROM incidents WHERE ST_DWithin(incident_location, 'POINT(-73.98534 40.748817)', 1000) = true
SELECT incident_id, response_time, response_description FROM incidents WHERE response_time > '5 minutes' ORDER BY response_time

SELECT incident_type, incident_time, incident_description FROM incidents WHERE vehicle_id = '87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321';

SELECT DISTINCT incident_type FROM incidents;

SELECT incident_id, COUNT(*) as response_count FROM responses GROUP BY incident_id HAVING response_count > 3;

SELECT incident_id, description FROM incidents WHERE location = 'Highway';

SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name, protocol_description FROM safety_protocols ORDER BY protocol_name DESC;
SELECT r.response_id, r.response_timestamp, r.response_description, e.location FROM response_data r JOIN emergency_incidents e ON r.incident_id = e.incident_id;
SELECT incident_id, description FROM emergency_incidents WHERE incident_timestamp > '2021-06-01' ORDER BY incident_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM emergency_incidents WHERE location = 'New York' ORDER BY incident_timestamp DESC;
SELECT incident_id, description FROM emergency_incidents WHERE location = 'California' ORDER BY incident_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM response_data JOIN emergency_incidents ON response_data.incident_id = emergency_incidents.incident_id WHERE response_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY response_timestamp DESC;

SELECT ei.incident_timestamp, rp.response_timestamp, sp.protocol_name FROM emergency_incidents ei JOIN response_data rp ON ei.incident_id = rp.incident_id JOIN safety_protocols sp ON ei.location = sp.protocol_description WHERE ei.location = 'Texas' ORDER BY ei.incident_timestamp ASC;

SELECT ei.location, COUNT(rd.response_id) AS total_responses FROM emergency_incidents ei LEFT JOIN response_data rd ON ei.incident_id = rd.incident_id GROUP BY ei.location ORDER BY total_responses DESC;
